    "desc": "Say Hello to Your New Favorite Fish: Barramundi. The Better Fish® Barramundi by Australis Aquaculture is an award-winning white fish that's high in omega-3's and half the calories of salmon. Pure and healthy, a flexible favorite for chefs and cooks around the world.",
    "navbar": "CONTACT US\nWHOLESALE",
    "text": "Skip to content\nCONTACT US\nWHOLESALE\nOUR PRODUCTS\nABOUT US\nRECIPES\nBLOG\nFIND US\nIntroducing\nthe next\nwave of fish\nTRY BARRAMUNDI\nWant to eat more seafood, but tired of having salmon day after day? We get it!\nThe Better Fish® Barramundi is:\nDELICIOUS\nMild, buttery and sweet taste for even picky eaters\nNUTRITIOUS\nLean and clean protein with ample omega-3’s\nAMBITIOUS\nOcean farmed with less impact and more climate resiliency\nBarramundi: finally, the fish you’ve been waiting for.\nThe approachable taste, health benefits, and low environmental impact are just some of the reasons why people love The Better Fish®. Curious to learn more about this ancient species and its benefits?\nOUR FISH\nFAIR\nTRADE\nCERTIFIED\n<\nWHAT RESTAURANTS ARE SAYING\n“The great thing I love about The Better Fish® Barramundi is that it comes hassle free. It's deboned, skinless, and is so flexible as far as what it can be used for. The versatility of this fish is a chef's dream.”\n— JASMINE NORTON, EXECUTIVE CHEF & OWNER OF THE URBAN OYSTER\n>\n1\n2\n3\n4\nAS SEEN IN…\nExplore our retail lineup\nSWEET & MILD\nSimply Skinless\nHAND-CUT STRIPS\nCrispy Fish Tenders\nTOMATO & GARLIC\nTuscan Herb Butter\nZESTY & BRIGHT\nLemon Herb Butter\nSWEET & TANGY\nGarlic Teriyaki\nFIND A STORE\n\nALL PRODUCTS\nThe perfect fish for a changing world\nWe imagine a world where anyone can enjoy healthy, delicious seafood that supports environmental and social progress.\nOUR STORY\nOcean farming for a better food system\nWe pioneer innovative ocean farming to scale environmentally-conscious and socially-responsible practices.\nOUR MISSION\nBetter practices for better fish\nThe Better Fish® is committed to responsible ocean farming that supporting sustainable livelihoods, safe working conditions, environmental protection, and transparent supply chains.\nLEARN MORE\nBarramundi with tomato and olive\nRecipes for any occasion.\nQUICK & EASY\nWeeknight Staples\nVIEW RECIPES\nCROWD-PLEASERS\nFamily Meals\nVIEW RECIPES\nFESTIVE & FUN\nDinner Party Ready\nVIEW RECIPES\nBROWSE ALL RECIPES\nTHE BLOG\nThe Better Fish® Becomes Fair Trade Certified\nREAD POST\nWhy Should I Care About Omega-3s?\nREAD POST\n5 Mouthwatering Marinades for Fish\nREAD POST\nALL ARTICLES\nFeed your inbox with recipes, news, and offers\nOUR STORY\nOUR MISSION\nOUR FISH\nOUR PRODUCTS\nBLOG\nRECIPES\nCHEF VIDEOS\nFIND US\nFAQS\nCONTACT US\nWHOLESALE\nSHARE FEEDBACK\nCONSUMER SUPPORT\nPRIVACY POLICY\nCOOKIE POLICY\n© 2022 THE BETTER FISH®. THE BETTER FISH® IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF AUSTRALIS AQUACULTURE, LLC.",
